headline.print_headline: Luke Bryan Wins CMA Entertainer of the Year
headline.main: Luke Bryan Wins CMA Entertainer of the Year

lead_paragraph: Luke Bryan further cemented his country superstar status on Wednesday night with his first entertainer of the year trophy at the Country Music Association Awards.
